âœ… Migration Plan with DLoader
1.Analyze SQL schema
2.Design MongoDB schema (embed orders in users)
3.Configure DLoader connection to SQL and MongoDB
4.Map Users â†’ users collection
5.Map Orders â†’ embedded documents
6.Run DLoader migration
